[
  "Xia Zuoquan is a director of electrified transportation supplier BYD. \r\n",
  "Xia studied computer science in University of Science & Technology of Beijing from 1985 to 1987.",
  "He graduated from Guanghua School of Management of Peking University with an MBA in 2007.",
  "Xia worked in the Hubei branch of The People's Insurance Company before he joined BYD in 1997.",
  "BYD is also one of the world's largest suppliers of rechargeable batteries used in mobile phones."
]